|NPCID|67579| |NAME|Vian the Volatile| |LVL|Rank 1.2| |ABIL|133607,133293,133430,134740| |ST|(npc:67579) has three abilities.<br/><br/>(spell:133607) Releases a Fire Line dealing heavy Fire damage.<br/>(spell:134740) summons a fireball that moves around the arena, dealing heavy Fire damage. If (npc:67579) touches them, it increases his spell casting speed.<br/>(spell:133293) inflicts Fire damage.<br/><br/>Avoiding (spell:133607) is your main priority. It's easily avoided by moving out of it's path.<br/><br/>Also avoid all the fireballs from (spell:134740). These fireballs will increase over time. You can control where (npc:67579) is positioned, as he will always chase you. You want him to avoid the fireballs too, or he will gain faster casting speed.<br/><br/>Try not to interrupt (spell:133293), otherwise (npc:67579) will start using melee attacks, which are more damaging than (spell:133293).|	
