|NPCID|67678| |NAME|Dark Summoner| |LVL|Rank 7.2| |ABIL|133499,125212,133465| |ST|The (npc:67678) uses (spell:125212), which deals about 85k damage and can be interrupted.<br/><br/>The (npc:67678) has a powerful melee attack and summons (npc:67664) throughout the fight.<br/><br/>The (npc:67664) spawn about every 15 seconds, randomly around the arena. Killing a (npc:67664) allows you to attack the (npc:67678) for 20 seconds, while his immunity is down.<br/><br/>The (npc:67664) will kill you with one hit and they have a long melee range. They move slowly and don't have any abilities.<br/><br/>You will have a cone of light that shines in front of you (like a flashlight). If you aim this at a (npc:67664) it will stun it for several seconds, giving you enough time to kill it before it can melee you.<br/><br/><b>When a (npc:67664) appears, kill it, then DPS the (npc:67678) while he is vulnerable.<br/><b>While you are fighting, you also need to kite all the remaining ghosts with your flashlight.<br/><b>Interrupt (spell:125212)<br/><b>Have backup cooldowns/self heals to manage (spell:125212)<br/><b>Beware that a (npc:67664) can spawn anywhere, even right on top of you.|	
|NPCID|67424| |NAME|Battletron| |LVL|Rank 7.3| |ABIL|133015,133018,133038| |ST|(npc:67424) has two abilities<br/><br/>(spell:133038) deals about 45k damage and is used frequently.<br/>(spell:133015) creates 8 mines, that rotate in a cirle around (npc:67424).<br/><br/>Melee players can detonate the mines by touching them, whereas ranged players use their spells to detonate them. Any spell or ability that passes through, or close enough to a mine will cause a detonation.<br/><br/>Detonating a mine deals a lot of damage to you (about 90k).<br/><br/>To win this fight, purposefully detonate 2-3 mines, forming a gap in the circle. Stand in the gap and DPS (npc:67424). You will need to constantly keep moving around to avoid detonating more mines.<br/><br/>DO NOT detonate more than 3 mines, or else (npc:67424) will re-summon all 8 mines.<br/><br/>This is a tough fight where you are constantly moving.|	
|NPCID|67573| |NAME|Meatball| |LVL|Rank 7.4| |ABIL|134911,134850| |ST|Throughout the fight (npc:67573) drops purple orbs on the ground around the arena. These orbs heal you by a large amount and give you a damage buff that stacks really high. (npc:67573) has really high health, so this stacking buff is needed to defeat him.<br/><br/>After a short time (npc:67573) will enrage and become (spell:134911).<br/><br/>You don't have to worry about any damage from (npc:67573), as you are constantly being healed from the orbs.<br/><br/>If you can't DPS and collect orbs while running around, then it's best to spend time at the start of the fight collecting orbs. Then use all your cooldowns once you have about 20 stacks of the buff, and burn down (npc:67573).<br/><br/>Easy fight, especially after (npc:67424)|	
